description: A short fan made quiz of 5 questions from a catalog of 40 examining the star wars universe. These are not a simple set of questions but ones that will test your the force within you. In no way is this app associated with Lucasfilm/Disney or endorsed by it. It has been made by fans for fans of the series. the skill is provided free of charge and generates no revenue for its creator.
